videos.description: Rashard Kelly cuts through the paint and is fed underneath by Shaquille Morris for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Wichita State feed underneath leads to jam

videos.description: Wichita State takes the lead right at the half thanks to Landry Shamet's long-distance bucket before the buzzer.
videos.headline: Shamet drains long three before halftime

videos.description: Darral Willis Jr. gets the pass and goes right up the vacant lane for the slam.
videos.headline: Shockers go right up the middle for dunk

videos.description: Landry Shamat drives the lane, goes up tough in between two Cowboys and drops in the layup while falling to the ground after the foul.
videos.headline: Shamat makes falling-down layup and the foul

videos.description: Lindy Waters III snags the Shockers' pass and goes end-to-end for a dunk.
videos.headline: Cowboys turn steal in to fast-break throwdown
